article_title: Community Health Centers gears up for expanded Medi-Cal program
article_text: As part of the Affordable Care Act, about 1 million more low-income adult Californians may be eligible for Medi-Cal, including as many as 19,000 SLO County residents. Community Health Centers' 26 clinics is on the front lines to provide primary care locally.
